# Large raw/ML binaries -> Zenodo, not GitHub (envi, cubes, references)
zenodo_data/
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.zip

# NOTE: small derived data ARE tracked in git on purpose and must NOT be ignored:
#   data/cube_products/**/  (masks, previews, cluster labels/model — .npy/.png)
#   data/wavelengths/*.npy
#   data/augmentation/cache_*/*.npz   (the exact AE/GAN fold caches used in the paper)
# Only the large raw/ML cubes (under zenodo_data/, ignored above) stay out of git.

